{"tid":817383,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(Netflix神作推介) 黑色喜劇Bojack Horseman","createTime":"2018-09-13T10:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T00:15:14.000Z","uid":33734,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3ad0d10ddd27617157785e2e1a50dbeeba5facd8","tid":817383,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T10:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://f4.bcbits.com/img/a2983687285_10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff4.bcbits.com%2Fimg%2Fa2983687285_10.jpg&h=728a6977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢套係一套動畫,唔好以為因為係動畫就好無聊/低B<br />\n佢描寫人嘅心理十分出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以話係近年將mental illness 演繹得最好嘅劇集<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(咩13 reasons個d就唔好提啦)</span>除此以外,仲有講到槍械管理,女權,退休軍人等政治議題.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4GTaApg29kRt32FrSJVgIPqPS8M=/0x0:1920x1080/1200x675/filters:focal(705x342:1011x648)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/58162673/1351058_1419981_zoomed.0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2F4GTaApg29kRt32FrSJVgIPqPS8M%3D%2F0x0%3A1920x1080%2F1200x675%2Ffilters%3Afocal%28705x342%3A1011x648%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_image%2Fimage%2F58162673%2F1351058_1419981_zoomed.0.png&h=18489290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBojack Horseman係一個過氣嘅明星馬,活係一個動物同人類共住嘅世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-603252ae823f6ce2c4b6d6a03ba69120_hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic1.zhimg.com%2F80%2Fv2-603252ae823f6ce2c4b6d6a03ba69120_hd.jpg&h=e27b8170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本上成個故事就係圍繞佢尋找自我嘅過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時4個配角面對各自問題嘅回應<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成套野最出色嘅地方係佢用動畫黎包裝,加埋擬人化嘅動物,用幽默黎同角色內心嘅黑暗做對比.令到觀眾睇套野嘅時候,長期感到好壓抑同無能為力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係呢個正正就係Bojack Horseman嘅優勝之處<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信如果套野係真人/全人類,一定會冇而家咁好睇<br />\n<br />\n無論你有冇mental illness,睇完套劇一定會對個病有更多嘅了解,甚至可以認清你自己嘅內心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會有好大反思<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一季頭六集可能會比較悶,但係之後會愈來愈精彩<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">/sad<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日就會出第五季,想追嘅快d把握機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n呢個po當宣傳吓俾未聽過BJ嘅人,睇過嘅盡量唔好劇透la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第五季討論區:<a href=\"https://lih.kg/bzNEBS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/bzNEBS</a>"},{"pid":"199dba3262ccca24af615a6fcc268f4766206e55","tid":817383,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad145c4285171eefe70a102b5836dc13d4362d8","tid":817383,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb35ced75147fa1bbb89a515cfe5dcfb476dab4","tid":817383,"uid":112666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇<br />\n好笑得黎又好sad"},{"pid":"2ab173cd529797a67839d3f89d7ed96c7d545e04","tid":817383,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fb35ced75147fa1bbb89a515cfe5dcfb476dab4","tid":817383,"uid":112666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇<br />\n好笑得黎又好sad"},"